        "generateUrl": "https://www.ziprecruiter.com/partner/documentation/",
        "setup": "Contact [ZipRecruiter ATS Integrations](mailto:atsintegrations@ziprecruiter.com) to register as a partner. Per the [Partner Integration Toolkit](https://www.ziprecruiter.com/partner/documentation/), the flow is: register as a partner, receive an API key, then use it in the `Authorization` header as `Basic YOUR_API_KEY` as described in [Authentication](https://www.ziprecruiter.com/partner/documentation/authentication/). If your HTTP client asks for Basic Auth `username`/`password`, the docs say to decode the key they provide.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
